text: Ommerenveld is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is a part of the municipality of Buren, and lies about 6 km northeast of Tiel. The statistical area "Ommerenveld", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 320.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005.
